<br>
Here is my contribution to the cause:<br>
Kurns Tower - undead do not agro and are spaced enough that you can take them down one at a time.  Burynai usually will not frenzy and when they do the pet disposes of them.<br>
<br>
Najena - Everything in here can be solod, safe place, other than the fact by Rathyl the pathing makes the pet poof and reappear on the first floor.<br>
<br>
Befallen - No comment this is ultra green, I have escorted groups in their teens.<br>
<br>
Blackburrow - see Beffalen<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Now my point is that I want to know where I can go solo.  Usually if I group I don't mind taking on Old Sebilis, Sol BB, LGuk or similar.  It's also useful when I escort a lower level group on a raid, it's useful to know if they totally screw up I can save them from a complete wipeout.<br>
<br>
<br>
Any more suggestions?<br>
Thanks.<br>
